TI  - Does Vocal Fatigue Negatively Affect Low Vocal Range in Professional, Female Opera Singers? A Survey Study and Single-Subject Pilot Study
PY  - 2024
T2  - Journal of Voice
VL  - 38
IS  - 3
SP  - 688
